hénoménologique. Cet ouvrage suscitera naturellement l’intérêt de la personne qui a subi un AVC de même que celui des gens de son entourage qui demeurent les sujets les plus concernés par cette pathologie.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aCerebrovascular diseasexTreatment. 0aCerebrovascular disease. 7aMEDICAL / Nursing / General.2bisacsh1 aGaulin, Philippe, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311127365508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017z978311127619940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276373322740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763733227423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763733227/original  a978-3-11-127365-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-127619-9  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles